elements.name: Add a new premise via traditional Premise +

steps.name: I enter credentials.user into input field c2m.username
I enter credentials.pass into input field c2m.password
I enter "/add premise" into input field home.universal_search_bar
I select "Apartment/Condo" option by text from dropdown premisepage.addpremise_search_by_list
I enter "78001" into input field premisepage.addpremise_zipcode_details
I press "TAB" key into input field premisepage.addpremise_zipcode_details
I select "California" option by text from dropdown premisepage.cis_division
I press "TAB" key into input field premisepage.cis_division
I put random address into input field premisepage.addpremise_address_details
I enter "San Francisco" into input field premisepage.addpremise_city_name
I enter "CA" into input field premisepage.addpremise_state_name
I wait 10 seconds for element premisepage.misc to display
I select "San Francisco, California" option by text from dropdown premisepage.trend_area
